  "name": "Red Butchers",
  "titles": "Red Butchers",
  "lore": "Clad in specially modified Terminator plate, designed to serve as both a protective, ablative armour but also as a restraint and confinement system, the Red Butchers are World Eaters driven beyond simple rage by their cranial implantations known as the Butcher’s Nails, rendering them into raving beasts that crave only violence. Thrashing against their bonds, and able only to exercise a marginal degree of control over their actions, these warriors are fit only to be unleashed upon the enemy as berserkers, freed from the concerns of military strategy and solely focused on violently dismembering their foes in a murderous frenzy.",
